      "rationale": "Use error assessment is not required at Model Risk Level 2 for this factor combination. Scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4 guidance. Assigned Gradation 1 by default."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection justified with sensitivity analysis; hemolysis damage model documented with literature support.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published comparative studies for rotating machinery hemolysis prediction. Power-law hemolysis damage model (Giersiepen et al.) used with documented constants. Sensitivity analysis comparing SST k-omega against realizable k-epsilon showed < 6% variation in hemolysis index. Model form meets Gradation 2."
    },
