      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Blood viscosity, density, and pump geometry inputs documented with uncertainty ranges; sensitivity of QoI to key inputs quantified.",
      "rationale": "Blood rheological properties sourced from published literature with uncertainty ranges. Pump geometry from manufacturer CAD with dimensional tolerances documented. One-at-a-time sensitivity analysis shows hemolysis index sensitivity to viscosity (±4%) and rotational speed (±7%) within acceptable bounds. Meets Gradation 2."
    },
